### Login de usuário
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/user/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "leon@test.com",
  "password": "senhasegura"
}


### criando um curso
POST https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/course HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
content-type: application/json

{
    "name":"Tecnico em Loistica",
    "description" : "O curso Técnico ",
    "workload": 2000,
    "ranking": 6, 
    "urlImg":"https://leschefsacademia.com.br/upload/09092020124641.png",
    "fieldOfStudy":"Tecnologia"
    
}

